	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Okay this is all the information I've gathered on the Bard Particle Quest.<BR>
<BR>
1.The starting NPC is Baldric Slezaf and his is located in the Dreadlands.  He wants pg 24 and Pg 25 of a symphony along with an instrument<BR>
<BR>
2. Konia Swiftfoot in WK asks you to deliver torches for her. You must run to Misty Thicket and hand it to Fajio Knejo right at the wall. Then run to South Ro zone entrance to swamp and pass it to Andad Filla and finally run to Lake Rathe near Arena zone where you get Proof of speed. Bring back to Konia and she only gives you the top half of the page.  She mentions a signature of importance on the bottom half and says an instrument belonging to Mahlin would be equivelent.  Not sure where to go from here<BR>
<BR>
3. Kelkim Menkia in SK will give you a quest to kill Edric the old in skyfire, Nezekezena in the Burning Woods, and Blackwing in the Rathe mtns to obtain Pg 25<BR>
<BR>
4. You must kill Quag Malestrom in the OOT and obtain a horn from him.  Give this horn to Vedicoat at the BB docks and you will get a note to give to Forpar to START the quest for the instrument:)<BR>
<BR>
5.  Forpor Fizfla (forgot where he was near steamfont I think) give note to him and he will give you a quest to obtain Kedge Backbone (Phin), Petrified Werewolf Skull (drovlag Warlord), Amygdalon tendral(warrior in fear plane), and the note back to him for half of the instrument.  Upon completing this half he gives you another quest to obtain a white and red dragon scale.  I assume you get these from the dragons:)  Hope this helps<BR>
<BR>
Kalamil Goldenote 33 circle
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
